# Cursor index exclusions — faster agents and lower token burn.
# Git ignores workspace clones (.gitignore); Cursor still indexes gitignored
# paths unless they are listed here.

# Managed-project clones (node_modules, builds, often 100k+ files)
workspace/
!workspace/README.md

# Local / vendored tool trees (usually untracked)
.agents/
.gstack/
.impeccable/

# Common dependency and build artefacts (if present outside workspace/)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.next/
**/target/
**/__pycache__/
